Class ClientProtocolHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • ss.pentago.network.protocol.ClientProtocolHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProtocolHandler
    public class ClientProtocolHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements ProtocolHandler
    ClientProtocolHandler receives messages from the Server and parses them. It tells the Client what to do.
